        },
        {
            "id": "02aa7221-cab7-4804-8cfa-31db6e5094e7",
            "content": "When it is necessary to share credentials with another person, it should be done through Bitwarden, or a secure communication channel such as Signal, and messages containing credentials should be deleted on both devices upon successful reception. Please remember that Emails are inherently not secure.",
            "tags": [
                {
